---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Now">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-xs font-mono text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Now</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl leading-tight mb-4">What I'm up to</h1>
      <p class="text-sm font-mono text-muted">Updated May 2026 — College Station, TX</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12 max-w-xl">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-mono text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Building</p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">This personal website. Just shipped the rebuild using Astro,
        Terraform, and GitHub Actions, all hosted on AWS. Documenting the rebuild itself as my most
        recent project.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-mono text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Reading</p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">The <em>Red Rising Saga</em>. I finished the trilogy and am
        currently on the sequel series, with the first book <em>Iron Gold</em>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-mono text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Learning</p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">After diving deeper in the cloud by obtaining my AWS Associate
        Solutions Architect, I wanted to expand my knowledge of AI (deeper than my AWS AI cert) so I'm
        picking up Agentic AI (Openclaw, Hermes).</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-ink/10">
      <p class="text-sm text-muted">
        Inspired by <a
          href="https://nownownow.com"
          class="text-maroon hover:underline underline-offset-2"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >nownownow.com</a>. Updated monthly — staleness is the failure mode.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
